Package: paf
Type: Package
Title: Income Polarization Index
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-02-20
Authors@R: person("Michail", "Tsagris", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mtsagris@uoc.gr")
Author: Michail Tsagris [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Michail Tsagris <mtsagris@uoc.gr>
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: Rfast, Rfast2, stats
Description: The PaF income polarization index as proposed by Duclos J. Y., Esteban, J. and Ray D. (2004). "Polarization: concepts, measurement, estimation". Econometrica, 72(6): 1737--1772. <doi:10.1111/j.1468-0262.2004.00552.x>. The index may be computed for a single or for a range of values of the alpha-parameter. Bootstrapping is also available.
License: GPL (>= 2)

